{"tid":492373,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[暫時得An]LayereD Stories 0 又可以刷首抽","createTime":"2017-12-07T12:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T01:04:00.000Z","uid":31242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ff3b720f6df8a034ace510fc30649b66e679c390","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:58:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3DoWdIt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3DoWdIt.png&h=c47dc826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岩岩出嘅新game，啲囡囡幾正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OMDgCrn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOMDgCrn.png&h=2e25bf09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAn: <a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/5625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F5625&d=JuSqV6q%2F1Y4mZ39y%2BfMHc7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=c1c76c64\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/5625</a><br />\nIOS: 官方話準備緊<br />\n<br />\n玩法係帶一隊人出去，4個正選2個後備，每turn 4個正選揀2個攻擊，回合制game<br />\n攻擊方法叫做有啲特點，係你撳住畫面果陣佢會出個圈，之後好似啲節奏game咁睇時機放手就打人<br />\n撳嘅同時可以左右郁角度令到攻擊路徑食到空中果啲一粒粒野，可以痛啲/補血，如果路徑上有自己人就好似會扣自己血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他野同一般game大同小異，都係果啲強化進化突破<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n抽角好似有原生4星同3升4嘅4星，前者可以上5星，後者最高就4星，抽完就無得再進化<br />\n不過哩啲其實都只係我估，因為我頭先抽完21抽都係得6隻3升4，除左佢送果兩隻之外暫時未見過可以上5星嘅4星<br />\n<br />\n難得嘅係岩岩出但竟然未瘋狂main<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過首抽過程有啲長，依家有啲時間睇下有無人有興趣一齊抽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c9891a170cd32ed3f874eb154c21bab519c78b","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/210607_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F210607_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d2c3a625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/210618_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F210618_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ab774763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/210628_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F210628_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=934ccc10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時打算剩刷下頭10抽先,要抽第二個10抽都幾晒時間下"},{"pid":"2191ce0e3f0cddd43600c7b3c8243a44b7705476","tid":492373,"uid":129787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:14:50.000Z","msg":"淨係中左隻霧鳴彩十 好想刷都幾次試下運 但係又嫌時間太長好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70202f696522685369e3dbe569635efe0e0eb599","tid":492373,"uid":129787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:15:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係中左隻霧鳴彩十 好想刷多幾次試下運 但係又嫌時間太長好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"85177aa0530c062a058223e5fa668e050543b8b5","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:16:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係中左隻霧鳴彩十 好想刷都幾次試下運 但係又嫌時間太長好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好想抽封面內田CV果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1568b2a7b90756a6d2f22c40aa69c2ce168b89a2","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/212117_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F212117_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=29a094af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自己抽完都覺得痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n決定認真玩下哩隻game<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b668b82bee97e581dbc7941d0b05737c7c5100","tid":492373,"uid":129787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:23:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/212117_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F212117_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=29a094af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自己抽完都覺得痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n決定認真玩下哩隻game<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一次刷幾耐 俾你搞到心思思想刷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e047bfb8625147f1feb13d0832872b27e95cb36","tid":492373,"uid":133875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:24:18.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"6a85876e1ac64089f7fc2422769508ba6467290b","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:26:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/212117_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F212117_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=29a094af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自己抽完都覺得痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n決定認真玩下哩隻game<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一次刷幾耐 俾你搞到心思思想刷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n剩刷頭10抽就好快，最晒時間係down data<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nskip對話，打一場(3wave)之後出黎再skip對話，再down data<br />\n<br />\n用最多時間都係download<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f39a5b439586bebeeffee2f127cf403fa025c6","tid":492373,"uid":23438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:29:51.000Z","msg":"留名等IOS"},{"pid":"6653e146eab087e4c8e6c20dffe4085748a4669a","tid":492373,"uid":129787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:30:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/212117_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F212117_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=29a094af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自己抽完都覺得痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n決定認真玩下哩隻game<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一次刷幾耐 俾你搞到心思思想刷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n剩刷頭10抽就好快，最晒時間係down data<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nskip對話，打一場(3wave)之後出黎再skip對話，再down data<br />\n<br />\n用最多時間都係download<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即刻刷刷佢先 好想要你左一個隻5星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ebfe8c88a581fec432a8778da3a3f74cd567a6","tid":492373,"uid":124876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:30:42.000Z","msg":"我要ios呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4ed4bf46030c41df310c554e50b7207e46acd7","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ULpUQDY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FULpUQDY.png&h=d167cd34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貼下官方game圖"},{"pid":"fa980a2c4572edcd90ac211d36c13764616fdbdd","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:32:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名等IOS</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>我要ios呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nApp Store版はただ今サービス開始に向けて準備中ですのでもう少々お待ちください。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab2e67c5ff1303eec804435c06171b6a999e408","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:32:53.000Z","msg":"官方咁講我估都係搞緊上架啲野嘅啫，相信耐極有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865ec18a7cdeeec425cef32736ee1ed4edd3453d","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:49:28.000Z","msg":"4星率寫24%，但實際上可以升5星嘅得6.634%"},{"pid":"9e57b014d452930b39cecde8d066094811186cf6","tid":492373,"uid":102700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/215322_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F215322_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=b7cf85a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/215330_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F215330_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1da8264e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廿抽左"},{"pid":"6cfb4fee9ecddac360f56cadf25fa68d3780217a","tid":492373,"uid":133875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:55:32.000Z","msg":"iOS 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b037a6364b5605065f9498ccf60c81d930f166f","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:57:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/215322_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F215322_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=b7cf85a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/215330_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F215330_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1da8264e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廿抽左</blockquote><br />\n都唔錯，battle sup都各有一隻原生4星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af1878ef44f94ace2f79e0b2af25b952c123f13","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>iOS 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed63727e51d17812ab0129d4dad44d2efadd3272","tid":492373,"uid":23438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:14:41.000Z","msg":"開模擬器玩住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b558130a8c8c0e29de78f19457d9f1573851c44f","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"每打完一章就會免費送一抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重複打01-05會有額外獎勵，打30次就可以拎齊，我估應該所有尾關都有哩類野farm<br />\n<br />\n左上個昇格我都仲係未太明，條bar滿左之後會出5個任比你解，解完就會昇rank，無留心睇有咩意義<br />\n<br />\n右下有個叫cluster嘅系統，未明做咩，隻game都幾多野下"},{"pid":"918694c3088aa7f36862d14d485a473137f0055e","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:22:55.000Z","msg":"support角除左自動技(帶左就有用)，主動技(夠turn先開得)，仲有個叫Active command (AC)<br />\nbattle果4條友上面有3條bar，暫時仲未太明點樣滿佢，總之滿左就可以開active command，類似技，但係都要瞄準，不過唔使玩節奏<br />\n<br />\n另外空中果啲一粒粒唔係全部都加攻，有啲會減攻，同攻擊果條友有關<br />\n即係有時上一隻係加攻，下一隻反而會減攻，要留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be696dfa9a0c952af9719f9b73deec2739471347","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:39:13.000Z","msg":"cluster好似係將啲玩家random咁分唔同組，之後一齊解任，然後過一段時間就打raid boss(依家就係42日後)，我都唔太明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 頭先唔知點解個back掣click完就消失左，卡死左係曜日果度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過重開game就無事了"},{"pid":"c8eb5e375847abd6ff5bfbb00d3bf7d5c5d83dad","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:51:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f769bfe6c27daacda8e9bf54cc1f03f8a1a592ee","tid":492373,"uid":36026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/000409_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F000409_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=b6904705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想問下咩事 唔識日文"},{"pid":"e5337c33278fa1116dca9676a522590f60cd78f5","tid":492373,"uid":89025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/001536_d802aa2041597e4a0b94ba689439f9a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F001536_d802aa2041597e4a0b94ba689439f9a3.jpg&h=542b77c1&s={SIZE}\" />IOS咁撚樣既"},{"pid":"f758f0833a2154386c488220002a38bfeef49fa0","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:25:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/001536_d802aa2041597e4a0b94ba689439f9a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F001536_d802aa2041597e4a0b94ba689439f9a3.jpg&h=542b77c1&s={SIZE}\" />IOS咁撚樣既</blockquote><br />\n係，ios未開ser<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f9bf1cf80fede4b05ec65ece87d0f2e9a255b6","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:26:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/000409_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F000409_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=b6904705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想問下咩事 唔識日文</blockquote><br />\n佢話你如果入唔到game/有咩問題嘅話可以試下轉日本時區解決<br />\n我個人無搞任何野都正常玩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9031ccbc11926a9a4c1b327bea5a2d7feac879ec","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T18:26:12.000Z","msg":"認真睇左次說明，cluster係將玩家random咁分組一齊解任/打boss嘅系統<br />\n解任方面自己解完有獎勵，全個cluster解晒任人數達一定數量會有個叫cluster chip嘅加成道具，有咩加成好似人人都唔同，例如岩岩我拎左個兩倍錢嘅<br />\n加成有限時，好似2粒鐘?無留心睇，而且一定要24小時內用<br />\n<br />\n戰鬥果方面每個角色每round可以攻擊次數都唔同，你要睇張卡上面有幾多格藍色嘅野(Slot)，每一回合隨機1-3格，所以有啲人會打3下，有啲打1下<br />\n<br />\n空中果啲一粒粒加攻定減攻睇打手屬性，同屬會加多啲，剋屬會減攻，無關係屬性就加少少攻<br />\n之後仲會有所謂嘅屬性牆，都係類似嘅野，由於啲加成直接乘上base dmg，所以都幾重要下<br />\n<br />\n相同角色自食可以加運(影響crit率，跌item etc)，但因為4星/5星滿星滿lv之後有個叫限界突破嘅野都要自食3次，所以唔建議咁快食<br />\n另外限界突破好似剩係得4/5星嘅battle角有，support好似唔關事...佢簡介寫得好唔清唔楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外support角係極難用，一定要睇配合，我抽左2隻原生4星，但完全用唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一隻係紫攻buff但全體扣1半血，一隻係綠buff攻其他屬全部減攻，完全唔岩用<br />\n送果隻女主係最泛用，全體加血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋隻game啲體回得勁撚慢，好似10分鐘1體?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隻game玩法都叫幾特別，如果打降臨/raid果啲可能都會好玩，平時都可以auto休閒，而且啲囡囡真係幾正，暫時應該都會玩一段時間<br />\n<br />\n不過暫時未知道突滿5星同突滿4星分別有幾大，如果後者都可以正常玩到嘅話都算良心game，話晒成2x%出率，一次10連起碼2~3金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8d959829569665973058b5f0082e2918e57705","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T18:27:07.000Z","msg":"不過本來都好似無咩人想玩哩隻，依家又剩係得An服，應該都係無咩人理架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n官方快啲搞好IOS啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c542e5edf93994448e244c0cee4de76b35cba341","tid":492373,"uid":23438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T18:31:29.000Z","msg":"巴打真係好努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6109f522c1edcbc49b99185330ba008f6b25524b","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T18:36:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打真係好努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難得有隻game起手無點刷就做歐洲人，自然有興趣玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外因為隻game普通得黎都有唔普通嘅地方，所以都要花時間理解同研究，咪分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d75f40c5b4d895deea81782a9cee0fe6f743b7","tid":492373,"uid":52520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T20:24:11.000Z","msg":"驚都上埋架仲好意思未有ser    想點樣呀"},{"pid":"67a66fb153d3f0b99b7c069b86a785d3092303d2","tid":492373,"uid":102700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T00:33:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真睇左次說明，cluster係將玩家random咁分組一齊解任/打boss嘅系統<br />\n解任方面自己解完有獎勵，全個cluster解晒任人數達一定數量會有個叫cluster chip嘅加成道具，有咩加成好似人人都唔同，例如岩岩我拎左個兩倍錢嘅<br />\n加成有限時，好似2粒鐘?無留心睇，而且一定要24小時內用<br />\n<br />\n戰鬥果方面每個角色每round可以攻擊次數都唔同，你要睇張卡上面有幾多格藍色嘅野(Slot)，每一回合隨機1-3格，所以有啲人會打3下，有啲打1下<br />\n<br />\n空中果啲一粒粒加攻定減攻睇打手屬性，同屬會加多啲，剋屬會減攻，無關係屬性就加少少攻<br />\n之後仲會有所謂嘅屬性牆，都係類似嘅野，由於啲加成直接乘上base dmg，所以都幾重要下<br />\n<br />\n相同角色自食可以加運(影響crit率，跌item etc)，但因為4星/5星滿星滿lv之後有個叫限界突破嘅野都要自食3次，所以唔建議咁快食<br />\n另外限界突破好似剩係得4/5星嘅battle角有，support好似唔關事...佢簡介寫得好唔清唔楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外support角係極難用，一定要睇配合，我抽左2隻原生4星，但完全用唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一隻係紫攻buff但全體扣1半血，一隻係綠buff攻其他屬全部減攻，完全唔岩用<br />\n送果隻女主係最泛用，全體加血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋隻game啲體回得勁撚慢，好似10分鐘1體?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隻game玩法都叫幾特別，如果打降臨/raid果啲可能都會好玩，平時都可以auto休閒，而且啲囡囡真係幾正，暫時應該都會玩一段時間<br />\n<br />\n不過暫時未知道突滿5星同突滿4星分別有幾大，如果後者都可以正常玩到嘅話都算良心game，<span style=\"color: red;\">話晒成2x%出率，一次10連起碼2~3金</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/083157_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F083157_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=2cf51dce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"549333ce6127ed2c1b264667dd43c5211be16f15","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:33:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/083157_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F083157_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=2cf51dce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n慘左啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef916142979f82ad3ffb7ee146036c711d030e4","tid":492373,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:33:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驚都上埋架仲好意思未有ser    想點樣呀</blockquote><br />\n睇唔透,我仲以為係上架問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537567736073580f62458f87b71f9205e6be3337","tid":492373,"uid":89025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:09:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>驚都上埋架仲好意思未有ser    想點樣呀</blockquote><br />\n睇唔透,我仲以為係上架問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n歧視IOS"},{"pid":"ceda68f627683d186db42757df36db58d5a567aa","tid":492373,"uid":116606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T04:00:10.000Z","msg":"有無人用18:9手機睇唔哂個畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103e7bd594022ad201624228ec800a11b6d6d075","tid":492373,"uid":23662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited